Casting this spell consumes material components equal to at least [[50c|money]]; for example, the powder of a crushed black pearl. A sphere of negative energy ripples out in a 60-foot-radius sphere from a point within 150 feet. Each creature in that area suffers extreme [[necrotic damage|damage type]].